{
  "stem": "676.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That must have been already 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We got her through to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next people to go was myself and my younger brother, Nathan, who was a year and a half younger than me, and a cousin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Her name was Gitcha Nagel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the three of us were supposed to be smuggled to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, when we came to the border, where we were supposed to go through the forest, a guide, the Polish guide-- they were paid for in advance, half in advance and half after we would be delivered to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Well, when we, when we got into the forest during the night, it was very, very scary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, it was dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the searchlights were going all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the dogs were barking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it was just terribly terrifying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The branches were scratching us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we were bloody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And my oldest cousin, she refused to go on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She was so terrified that she said, just leave me here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And just let me die here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I just don't want to go on anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "My little brother couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was just-- he just couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He just refused to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I, all of-- I think maybe I must have been 11 or 12-- I just had to drag them and beg them, just we will be soon there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Please hold on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We'll be soon there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The guide refused to go on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He said, I'm not going any further because they're going to get us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You hear the dogs, and you see the searchlights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And if they catch us, not only you will be killed-- shot-- but I will be shot, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
